channel.title: What should I sell?
channel.description:
What should I sell?
Ok, so I purchased a new server machine for $15.50 (http://www.trademe.co.nz/Browse/Listing.aspx?id=177787965)
Now, I have 3 server machines. I am thinking of selling one. Here are the specs of the two that I might sell:
Compaq Deskpro EN series. Ram: 512MB SD100 CPU: Intel PII 500MHZ HDD: 50GB @ 7.2K RPM Network Interface: dual Ethernet Cards at 280gbps OS: Windows Server Enterprise 2003 PSU: 250 Watt Volume: Can not hear at all I originally payed: $0 - Found outside
Compaq Proliant DL380 / Aus Ram: 512MB SD133 CPU: Intel PIII 733MHZ HDD: 2x 18.2GB @ 10K RPM / 9.1GB @ 10K RPM Network Interface: 1x Onboard at 10mbps / 1x Card at 100mbps OS: Windows Server Enterprise 2003 PSU: Dual PSU at unknown Watt Volume: Like 747 Taking off I originally payed: $36
Which one should I sell? How much for?
